# acknowledge()

**Instance Method**

Acknowledges a successful or failed job. Jobs must be acknowledged to free up space for [doc://com.apple.photokit/documentation/Photos/PHAssetResourceUploadJob/jobLimit].

## Declaration

```swift
func acknowledge()
```

## Processing jobs

- **retry(destination:)**: Retries a job that is failed, unacknowledged, and has not been retried before. Successful retries also free up space for [doc://com.apple.photokit/documentation/Photos/PHAssetResourceUploadJob/jobLimit].
